14.IN which senario we will go for site-to-site vpn  and Expressroute ?
Site-to-Site VPN - (A Site-to-Site VPN connects your on-premises network to AWS over the public Internet using an IPsec VPN tunnel)
Use Cases
Quick, low-cost connectivity to AWS
Non-latency-sensitive workloads
Backup, development, or test environments
Small-scale production workloads where moderate bandwidth is enough

ExpressRoute:
ExpressRoute provides a private, dedicated connection between your on-premises network and Azure, bypassing the Internet.
Use Cases
Mission-critical production workloads
High-performance applications (ERP, databases, SAP, SAP HANA)

